&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant in Adult Community Psychiatry - 10 PAs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Berkshire Healthcare NHS Foundation Trust are seeking a Consultant Psychiatrist to become part of a multidisciplinary team serving a diverse population predominantly in the South of Reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is mostly working with those requiring a longer intervention and assessing new referrals (Common Point of Entry). As such the post holders will hold a key role in providing medical care and leadership at the crucial early stages of intervention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information about this post please contact Ralph Chananda (Head of Mental Health Services) on 07500607 020 or Dr Mark Parry (Consultant Psychiatrist) on 0118 960 5389&lt;/p&gt;
